{"tid":1979892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"批鬥完未 日日睇你地互批好撚攰","createTime":"2020-04-19T17:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T18:37:39.000Z","uid":139294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c36374c187b271c2717bcb5dc3371911b31566b9","tid":1979892,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"To 手足<br />\n<br />\n由黃店 到 議員 到 youtuber 再到文宣page<br />\n日日都見到大家係到嘈同互屌<br />\n收手啦好嗎<br />\n包容係咪真係好難<br />\n人血饅頭 呃人撚 屌 係好應該<br />\n但有時啲野細撚到仆街都要屌一餐......<br />\n光復香港未做到 內部就已經搞成咁<br />\n人地港共都笑鳩我地唔成氣候啦<br />\n一人少一句啦大家<br />\n再係咁啲士氣就冇曬架啦<br />\n疫情已經令到大家既火熄左啲<br />\n我唔想再因批鬥而令到大家團火熄滅<br />\n謹言慎行 三思做人啊各位<br />\n好攰啦 冇謂再咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\nFrom 路人甲"},{"pid":"6dec991e6c66fba31c7df9f75fcf49ebc1820522","tid":1979892,"uid":135693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3f2f596ce28f6b6cef1e4aea685505eff9e7846f","tid":1979892,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dec991e6c66fba31c7df9f75fcf49ebc1820522","tid":1979892,"uid":135693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"引戰呀<br />\n內戰囉"},{"pid":"a4978297c41132226145edcb0c27bbebaf6026e0","tid":1979892,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">[行動Po] 手足整左網站- 2秒簽哂所有聯署！一齊簽！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1979857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1979857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"dec7e9cb188e3ae660cccfc4b75c16e8d58022c2","tid":1979892,"uid":235212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T18:37:39.000Z","msg":"啱呀 成撚日係到自己人屌自已人"}]}